commit 87d9a0b4e360f4c2fde401b6cd9d1677b487e1aa
Author: Deborah Dahl <dahl@conversational-technologies.com>
Date:   Mon Mar 2 15:46:57 2026 -0500

    updates to agents to refine interactive behavior
    
    Updated agent-side addressing so only the explicitly targeted agent handles to.speakerUri utterances, preventing non-addressed agents from responding. Also aligned conversational-name handling in the agent templates to use better sender-name resolution with fallback logic.
    Signed-off-by: Deborah Dahl <dahl@conversational-technologies.com>

diff --git a/agent-template/openfloor/agent.py b/agent-template/openfloor/agent.py
